Cntrl Shift O - automatically adds required imports

Generate getters and setters by right clicking->Source->Generate Getters and Setters.

IN Spring Boot, all the HTTP requests are handled by
controller classes.

Spring Data REST offers and easy and fast way to implement RESTful
Web Services with Spring. Need to add dependency. Able to define
the endpoint (url) of service in the properties file:
spring.data.rest.basePath=/api
localhost:8000/api

curl -X "DELETE" http://localhost:8000/api/cars/4
This will delete the car with id=4. (DELETE GET POST PUT).
Run from command line.